 '''while:'''
     The while statement lets you execute a series of
     statements while an expression evaluates to TRUE.

 '''Example:'''

 <nowiki>

 dilbegin foo();
   code
   {
     while (not self.inside) {
       exec("say I own nothing", self);
       pause;
     }
     exec("say ahh.. now i own something", self);
   }
   dilend</nowiki>

